Summary: Defines the properties for the VisualShaderNodeFloatFunc class, specifically its function type.

Properties
* function (Function): The mathematical function to apply. Possible values are:
    * FUNC_SIN (0): Sine.
    * FUNC_COS (1): Cosine.
    * FUNC_TAN (2): Tangent.
    * FUNC_ASIN (3): Arcsine.
    * FUNC_ACOS (4): Arccosine.
    * FUNC_ATAN (5): Arctangent.
    * FUNC_ATAN2 (6): Arctangent with two arguments.
    * FUNC_SINH (7): Hyperbolic sine.
    * FUNC_COSH (8): Hyperbolic cosine.
    * FUNC_TANH (9): Hyperbolic tangent.
    * FUNC_ABS (10): Absolute value.
    * FUNC_SQRT (11): Square root.
    * FUNC_FMOD (12): Floating-point remainder.
    * FUNC_POSITIVE_INFINITY (13): Positive infinity.
    * FUNC_NEGATIVE_INFINITY (14): Negative infinity.
    * FUNC_IS_INF (15): Checks if the value is infinity.
    * FUNC_IS_NAN (16): Checks if the value is Not-a-Number.
    * FUNC_FLOOR (17): Floor value.
    * FUNC_CEIL (18): Ceiling value.
    * FUNC_ROUND (19): Round to nearest integer.
    * FUNC_TRUNC (20): Truncate to integer.
