    * FUNC_SMOOTHSTEP (27): Smoothstep interpolation.
    * FUNC_ মসৃণ (28): Smoothstep interpolation (alternative name).
    * FUNC_DIFFERENCE (29): Difference between two values.
    * FUNC_DOT_PRODUCT (30): Dot product of two vectors.
    * FUNC_CROSS_PRODUCT (31): Cross product of two vectors.
    * FUNC_DISTANCE (32): Distance between two points.
